Ansible i3 Desktop Container


Usage

    $ make            # Build, run and configure the container 
    $ make ssh        # SSH into the container
    $ make stop       # Stop the container
    $ make uninstall  # Delete the container image
    

Ansible i3 Desktop Container Makefile Targets

    Setup

        Copy public SSH key from ~/.ssh.
        $ make setup

    Build

        Build Docker image.
        $ make build

    Run

        Run the new container.
        $ make run

    IP

        Print the running container IP address.
        $ make ip

    Ping

        Verify the container is running.
        $ make ping

    Hosts

        Generate Ansible hosts file.
        $ make hosts

    Check

        Verify the new image and the new container.
        $ make check

    Install

        Run the Ansible i3 playbook.
        $ make install

    SSH

        SSH into the container.
        $ make ssh

    Stop

        Stop the container.
        $ make stop

    Clean

        Remove temporary build files.
        $ make clean

    Uninstall

        Delete the container image.
        $ make uninstall


